{"tid":1035182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔見咗野求吓大家幫吓手","createTime":"2019-02-24T12:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T12:53:50.000Z","uid":238813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9db24134a1753b873b6fed238b09e3592696ba5c","tid":1035182,"uid":238813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"事發星期四我病到溫溫鄧鄧<br />\n夜晩七點幾上咗巴士30x 荃灣方向 總站落 應該唔小心漏咗個card holder喺車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但之後問返站長又話無執到失物<br />\n所以十成九都係比人執咗了唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個cars holder係男朋友送 charles and keith 粉綠粉紅色間隔款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面無咩值錢野 得張九十幾蚊既八達通 同身份證 學生證<br />\n但要全部申請過就好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己都衰大意 唔好好保管咁重要既野<br />\n 如果你執到又睇到個post 我唔介意你用哂張八達通既錢 淨係想搵返啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求吓你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437d957c29169a3a247293e935ff79d9e6113a15","tid":1035182,"uid":33185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc77d9d5a4f80464b77d16c7407210a765782d8","tid":1035182,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c4447d758f6731f631dd47cef88b6012a80cb8d","tid":1035182,"uid":238813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9568c58f312473e31ffa5869ebcaaa89d8aeb089","tid":1035182,"uid":2